142
00:24:51,125 --> 00:24:53,005
<i>Yo y el pequeño Joe
encontramos a Martin muerto.</i>

143
00:24:53,127 --> 00:24:55,562
<i>Te dije lo que vi durante el juicio.</i>

144
00:24:55,564 --> 00:24:57,764
<i>- Sally, has mentido.
- Little Joe,</i>

145
00:24:57,899 --> 00:24:58,932
